gomodel:SYNGO_2113  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 2: Arc antisense infusion 2 h after high-frequency stimulation blocks LTP consolidation.\n\n11/12/2017 Pim\n- Contrary to the claim of the authors I have not annotated the claimed role of Arc in the regulation of actin dynamics. Reason is that I do not see that this is a direct or a indirect mechanism of action for the Arc protein.. Experimental description: \"Data were obtained from 189 male Sprague Dawley urethane-anesthetized (1.4-1.8 g/kg, i.p.) rats weighing 250-320 g.\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4973-5732" ;
